what prob ci/cd solves
automation, faster release ,less manual work, early bug detection

Cron job - schedule the rerun of the program
used in jenkins to tell after how much time do you want to rerun or update changes


Github push ------> Maven build ---------> Sonarqube test -----> deploy to dev -----> deploy to QA ------> deploy to prod

RF -> roll forward, RB -> roll back
CHG request - label(change request)
labels are used when the deployment failed labels are used to identify the earlier versions and rolled back

RM - release management
PS - Production support
